## Escaping Closure

```swift
func performEscaping(closure: @escaping () -> ()) {
    print("start")

    DispatchQueue.main.asyncAfter(deadline: .now() + 3) {
        closure()
    }

    print("end")
}

performEscaping {
    print("closure")
}
```
